snippet: A series of car bombs targeting busy markets and shopping streets in and around Baghdad killed at least 51 people and wounded more than 100 on Tuesday, Iraqi medical and police sources said.
abstract: Series of car bombs targeting busy markets and shopping streets in and around Baghdad kill at least 51 people and wounded more than 100.
lead_paragraph: A series of car bombs targeting busy markets and shopping streets in and around Baghdad killed at least 51 people and wounded more than 100 on Tuesday, Iraqi medical and police sources said.

headline.main: Iraq: Dozens Die in Car Bombings in the Baghdad Area
